HSBC Global Sells 0.5% Stake in Emami Ltd. in Open Market

-- B y   A b h i s h e k   S h a n k e r
-- 
2011-09-15T14:08:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/hsbc-global-sells-0-5-stake-in-emami-ltd-in-open-market.html
HSBC Global Asset Management Ltd.
sold 711,703 shares or 0.5 percent of its stake in  Emami Ltd. (HMN)  in
the open market, according to an exchange filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
